model

Class CharacterBuild

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.CharacterBuild
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CharacterBuild
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Instances of this class represents the specific build character. It holds general information about the character and it is serialized along with the the lesser classes (Perk, Skill and Attribute) for saving the build on disk.
    Author:
    Vlada47
